"title": "8615: prayer, doubts about",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8615",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Sometimes God does not seem to answer prayer, causing his people to doubt him. Scripture affirms God's faithfulness to those who pray according to his will, and points out that the human understanding of a situation is limited.</p>\n<h2>Examples of God's servants questioning his promises</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:22-Exod5:23\">EXO 5:22–5:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:2-Gen15:3\">GEN 15:2–15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:7-Josh7:9\">JOS 7:7–7:9</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of God's servants questioning the tasks he has given them</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:11-Num11:15\">NUM 11:11–11:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:4\">1KI 19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:15-Jer15:18\">JER 15:15–15:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:7-Jer20:9\">JER 20:7–20:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:14-Jer20:18\">JER 20:14–20:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:1-Jonah4:3\">JON 4:1–4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:46\">MAT 27:46</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:34\">MRK 15:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1\">PSA 22:1</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of God's servants expressing their anger and confusion in prayer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:2-Job10:22\">JOB 10:2–10:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job13:20-Job13:27\">JOB 13:20–13:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:1-Job14:22\">JOB 14:1–14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps13:1-Ps13:2\">PSA 13:1–13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:9-Ps42:10\">PSA 42:9–42:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:22-Ps44:26\">PSA 44:22–44:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:7-Ps77:9\">PSA 77:7–77:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:4-Ps80:6\">PSA 80:4–80:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:6-Ps88:9\">PSA 88:6–88:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:2-Hab1:3\">HAB 1:2–1:3</a></p>\n<h2>God's response to prayers of questioning or complaint</h2>\n<h3>God reiterates his promises to those who question him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:2-Gen15:5\">GEN 15:2–15:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:1-Exod6:8\">EXO 6:1–6:8</a></p>\n<h3>God provides help for those who question him</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:1-1Kgs19:8\">1KI 19:1–19:8</a></p>\n<h3>God rebukes those who question him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:1-Job40:9\">JOB 40:1–40:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:19-Jer15:21\">JER 15:19–15:21</a></p>\n<h3>God explains events to those who question him</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:5-Hab1:11\">HAB 1:5–1:11</a></p>",
